{"tid":2516473,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有睇日本ニュース (日本1940年開始播嘅新聞)","createTime":"2021-05-04T16:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T00:50:41.000Z","uid":362393,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ea8a230dd249bdbd05959c04491c1a45a6ac12","tid":2516473,"uid":362393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"Link: <a href=\"https://www2.nhk.or.jp/archives/shogenarchives/jpnews/list.cgi?value=1942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.nhk.or.jp%2Farchives%2Fshogenarchives%2Fjpnews%2Flist.cgi%3Fvalue%3D1942&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=fbf51af2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.nhk.or.jp/archives/shogenarchives/jpnews/list.cgi?value=1942</a><br />\n呢排幫人做歷史研究做到傻左，之後識左d日本人，佢地就介紹左上邊條link比我<br />\n睇左之後，我覺得真係好撚正<br />\n以前睇documentary同British Pathe可能就睇得多，不過來自大日本帝國既戰爭宣傳，大家又有冇睇過？<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，去圖先<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcwH2wWSd1Px4fYGrujVCzhcXXnbRbpboZQqosuXrMYDN?filename=LDSBU4o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDSBU4o.png&h=deb16730&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n三年零八個月就聽得多，但係日本仔係點吹佢地係救世主？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSF87mX4NWJ1XNJAmfyvCbryTSa47LU1GAWbvKCr7zVza?filename=ci0jSRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fci0jSRy.png&h=4a33e03a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家可以試下由1940支那戰役開始睇，睇到1941香港同珍珠港，再睇到1945輸到冇片再播<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後日本投降，核彈廢墟等等，保證你情感肯定會有超強烈既起伏。<br />\n<br />\n唔係講笑，以前都未睇過d咁既野，睇左之後真係成個人成熟左，明白戰爭唔只係輸贏，而係一件兩敗俱傷既事黎；戰爭沒有贏家，只有輸得更慘更轟烈既輸家。"},{"pid":"1fafade23a9ad78548b4e2b8a4dbf92fd88527a5","tid":2516473,"uid":52046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T18:41:09.000Z","msg":"高質post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52eb7646f827cdd018ffdad6a99207edc1fae5b","tid":2516473,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T00:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}